text: Wara Wara is a 1930 Bolivian romantic drama movie directed by José María Velasco Maidana and stars Juanita Taillansier, Martha de Velasco, Arturo Borda, Guillermo Viscarra Fabre, Emmo Reyes. It was distributed by Urania Film. ==Other websites== * Category:1930 romantic drama movies Category:Bolivian movies Category:Silent movies Category:Movies set in the 16th century Category:Movies set in Bolivia
